Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Ethics Fairness Module Stub
Provides comprehensive algorithmic fairness assessment and intervention capabilities
Enables demographic parity, equalized odds, individual fairness, and intersectional analysis
:End Note

Type FairnessAssessmentSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    fairness_metrics as List[FairnessMetric]
    assessment_methods as List[FairnessAssessmentMethod]
    fairness_algorithms as List[FairnessAlgorithm]
    fairness_framework as FairnessFramework
    fairness_reporting as FairnessReporting
    system_configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type FairnessMetric is Dictionary with:
    metric_id as String
    metric_name as String
    metric_type as String
    metric_formula as String
    metric_interpretation as String
    metric_thresholds as Dictionary
    metric_validation as MetricValidation

Type FairnessAssessmentMethod is Dictionary with:
    method_id as String
    method_name as String
    method_type as String
    applicable_fairness_types as List[String]
    method_parameters as MethodParameters
    assessment_accuracy as Float
    computational_complexity as Float
    method_limitations as List[String]

Type FairnessAlgorithm is Dictionary with:
    algorithm_id as String
    algorithm_name as String
    algorithm_type as String
    algorithm_parameters as AlgorithmParameters
    algorithm_performance as AlgorithmPerformance
    algorithm_limitations as List[String]

Type FairnessFramework is Dictionary with:
    framework_id as String
    fairness_criteria as List[FairnessCriterion]
    fairness_methodologies as List[FairnessMethodology]
    fairness_metrics as List[FairnessMetric]
    fairness_reporting as FairnessReporting

Type FairnessReporting is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    reporting_templates as List[ReportingTemplate]
    reporting_formats as List[ReportingFormat]
    reporting_frequency as String
    reporting_automation as ReportingAutomation

Type AssessmentContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    data_context as Dictionary
    model_context as Dictionary
    fairness_requirements as Dictionary
    assessment_constraints as Dictionary
    context_metadata as Dictionary

Type FairnessContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    fairness_analysis_scope as Dictionary
    fairness_assessment_parameters as Dictionary
    fairness_criteria as Dictionary
    fairness_metadata as Dictionary

Type IntersectionalContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    intersectional_analysis_scope as Dictionary
    intersectional_parameters as Dictionary
    intersectional_constraints as Dictionary
    intersectional_metadata as Dictionary

Type CounterfactualContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    counterfactual_analysis_requirements as Dictionary
    counterfactual_parameters as Dictionary
    counterfactual_constraints as Dictionary
    counterfactual_metadata as Dictionary

Type FairnessAssessment is Dictionary with:
    assessment_id as String
    fairness_metrics as Dictionary
    fairness_analysis as Dictionary
    fairness_recommendations as List[String]
    assessment_confidence as Float
    assessment_metadata as Dictionary

Type InterventionContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    intervention_requirements as Dictionary
    intervention_constraints as Dictionary
    intervention_metadata as Dictionary

Type MonitoringContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    monitoring_requirements as Dictionary
    monitoring_frequency as String
    monitoring_parameters as Dictionary
    monitoring_metadata as Dictionary

Process called "create_fairness_assessment_system" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "assess_algorithmic_fairness" that takes fairness_system as Dictionary and assessment_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "assess_demographic_parity" that takes fairness_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "assess_equalized_odds" that takes fairness_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "assess_individual_fairness" that takes fairness_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_intersectional_analysis" that takes fairness_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "assess_counterfactual_fairness" that takes fairness_system as Dictionary and context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_fairness_interventions" that takes fairness_assessment as Dictionary and fairness_system as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "monitor_fairness_over_time" that takes fairness_system as Dictionary and monitoring_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_fairness_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_fairness_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 